{"tid":1337770,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"新牌出SUV選擇","createTime":"2019-07-21T10:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:36:22.000Z","uid":254620,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"497ab4026079ac8efe78c1c9280cc09aa1d70967","tid":1337770,"uid":254620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"新牌想買SUV<br />\n本身鍾意LEXUS UX, 但係OUT BUD同埋新牌驚易撞同刮花, 所以想買架2手 SUV 練下車先<br />\nbudget: $10-15萬<br />\n而家有幾個方向<br />\n<strong>1. 買6年以上SUV操車, 渣1-2年之後放售</strong><br />\n考慮點:<br />\na. 可選擇歐州及日本SUV (e.g. BMW X3, LEXUS RX270 etc)<br />\nb. 買架保值D方便易手<br />\nc. 6年以上多機會要修理同每年續牌<br />\n<strong>2. 買6年以內SUV, 渣夠6年放售</strong><br />\n考慮點:<br />\na. 唔洗每年續牌同埋維修機會較少<br />\nb. budget可選擇車款較少<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大多比D意見同有咩車款推介, 感激! <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f841dced0226ff9b053490d46732808d4f8f12","tid":1337770,"uid":216432,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"subaru xv<br />\n新車 199,800<br />\n四驅 CVT波箱<br />\n抵玩又安全"},{"pid":"9827dcd5539d6a7f540a739ca2099bcfcbd2322e","tid":1337770,"uid":55125,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:08:52.000Z","msg":"harrier啦<br />\n易整 又平 個車價已經見底執架full option/豪華版都唔冼十皮 龍唔新又唔舊 錶板靚仔 牌費又ok"},{"pid":"785cd260b0596056cca7e268929e98b6e87a8c56","tid":1337770,"uid":22224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:07:21.000Z","msg":"上代RAV4 10皮有部<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e075965ed7b7cf09b797a480a30e5cdd816c73c","tid":1337770,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:43:15.000Z","msg":"搵返架同UX近似嘅<br />\n例如係Vezel、RAV4、CR-V咁"},{"pid":"f4788c551c9412f8c06e4d68a926c3439931aadb","tid":1337770,"uid":13558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e075965ed7b7cf09b797a480a30e5cdd816c73c","tid":1337770,"uid":19